How to get pid of a process using a port
lsof -i tcp:3000


Uninstall MySQL on Mac OS X:
This was a life saver!
sudo rm /usr/local/mysql
sudo rm -rf /usr/local/mysql*
sudo rm -rf /Library/StartupItems/MySQLCOM
sudo rm -rf /Library/PreferencePanes/MySQL*
edit /etc/hostconfig and remove the line MYSQLCOM=-YES-
sudo rm -rf /Library/Receipts/mysql*
sudo rm -rf /Library/Receipts/MySQL*
sudo rm -rf /var/db/receipts/com.mysql.*


mysqldump -uroot -p --all-databases > alldb.sql
mysql -u root -p < alldb.sql

restart machine in case of any problem

MySQL5.5 and 5.6 difference
5.5 does not have STATS_PERSISTENT
so replace all STATS_PERSISTENT=0 with blank


